{"tid":1333594,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[721公測]香城online 小建議","createTime":"2019-07-19T18:27:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T09:53:23.000Z","uid":225739,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4cb931d6fd44af96ee9a5fa3bf9fbc2559d87551","tid":1333594,"uid":225739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:27:39.000Z","msg":"每人應該最少有一支血水<br />\n血水成分:<br />\nziplock (裝住) x1<br />\n生理鹽水10ml x1<br />\n7.5x7.5 cm (3&quot;) 紗布 x5<br />\n7.5cm(3&quot;) 繃帶 x1<br />\n黏貼膠布x5<br />\n<br />\n原因:補師未必可以即時去到奶,附近嘅人可以利用呢支血水去做臨時補血<br />\n另外:補師人手未必夠,簡單刷傷,小傷口就咁飲血水就ok<br />\n好處:價錢平唔洗點課金買,高效率,周圍嘅商店npc都有得買,減低補給角式嘅壓力"},{"pid":"31342576633b93d24a95e2ad41de5607e2a37ac4","tid":1333594,"uid":225739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T19:03:29.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b5bbe22e745008bec442eb54d2b25bb3d83371a3","tid":1333594,"uid":33215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T20:44:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c12ef7e235d2dfd5d194c5f1ec0c8db08ae41742","tid":1333594,"uid":63651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T09:53:23.000Z","msg":"Added"}]}